# Example HTTP requests for httpyum
# This file demonstrates the .http format with variables and various request types

@baseUrl = https://httpbin.org
@userId = 123
@token = test-api-key-12345

### Simple GET request
GET {{baseUrl}}/get

### GET with headers
GET {{baseUrl}}/headers
Accept: application/json
User-Agent: httpyum/0.1.0
X-API-Key: {{token}}

### GET with query parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/anything?user={{userId}}&format=json

### POST with JSON body
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "active": true
}

### POST with form data
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Jane+Doe&email=jane@example.com&userId={{userId}}

### PUT request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/put
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{userId}},
  "status": "updated"
}

### DELETE request
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/delete?id={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test different status codes - Success
GET {{baseUrl}}/status/200

### Test different status codes - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/status/404

### Test different status codes - Server Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/status/500

### Complex JSON response
GET {{baseUrl}}/json

### Very long response for testing scrolling
# This endpoint returns a large JSON response with many items
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Description: Returns 100 posts - great for testing scrolling functionality

### Large user list for testing
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users
Description: Returns user list with detailed information

### Very large comments list
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/comments
Description: Returns 500 comments - excellent for testing viewport scrolling
